@startuml d1-audio-lifecycle-states
!theme plain
skinparam shadowing false
skinparam state {
  BackgroundColor #E8F4FF
  BorderColor #2E5C8A
  FontStyle bold
  ArrowColor #2E5C8A
}

title Herold — D1 Audio document lifecycle (relative to its VoiceNote)

[*] --> bound : UC-05 Capture\n(audio persisted, audioPath set)

state bound
note right of bound
  Audio is streamable for the entire
  lifetime of the **VoiceNote** (UC-10).
  No retention timer, no processed-triggered
  cleanup, no pruning.
end note

bound --> [*] : UC-11 Delete\n(audio + VoiceNote removed together)

@enduml
